text:
="preserve">Dadang Wigiarto (20 December 1966 – 26 November 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was a member of the National Awakening Party. Wigiarto was born in Pasuruan, Indonesia. From 2010 until his death, he was Regent of the Situbondo Regency.
Wigiarto died of COVID-19 on 26 November 2020 in the Situbondo Regency at the age of 53.
